    Disk Utilization
    Status
            Can also set custom based metrics 

* 5 Min intervals, status will be updated



2 Major Issues:
    Instance Limit Exceeded error : Every region there will be a Top limit of EC2 instances that allowed to launch. By default it is 20, and can be upgradable
    InsufficientInstanceCapacity Error : AWS is out of the number of requested instances from the on Demand pool